OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Sophia Ankel
OL,8,FSince its full-scale invasion of two
OL,9,Fyears ago, has been accused of
OL,10,Fdeporting or displacing thousands of
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FThe children, who are seized from
OL,14,Fschools, orphanages and private homes,
OL,15,Fare allegedly brought to Russia or
OL,16,FRussian-held territories without their
OL,17,Fconsent.
