OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FThe mass abductions has led
OL,7,Fprosecutors at the International
OL,8,FCriminal Court to issue arrest
OL,9,Fwarrants in March 2023 for President
OL,10,FVladimir Putin and Russia's children's
OL,11,Frights commissioner, Maria Lvova-
OL,12,FBelova.
OL,14,FRussia, which does not recognise the
OL,15,Fcourt's authority, called the move
OL,16,Fmeaningless and opened its own
OL,17,Fcriminal cases against ICC prosecutors
OL,18,Fand judges.
