OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FRussia claims the children do not have
OL,7,Fparents or guardians to look after
OL,8,Fthem. Its state media portrays their
OL,9,Fso-called adoption as an act of
OL,10,Fgenerosity that gives new homes and
OL,11,Fmedical resources.
OL,13,FWhile officials regularly announce the
OL,14,Farrival of Ukrainian orphans in
OL,15,FRussian military planes, they do not
OL,16,Fgive official numbers on how many
OL,17,Fchildren it deports.
