OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Ukrainian government-
OL,7,Frun project Children of War reports
OL,8,Fthat at least 19,546 unaccompanied
OL,9,FUkrainian children have been displaced
OL,10,Fsince February 2022.
OL,12,FAmong the children was Sofia*, a 14-
OL,13,Fyear-old girl from Kherson who was
OL,14,Fseized by Russians in the first days
OL,15,Fof the full-scale invasion while
OL,16,Fstaying at her grandmother's house in
OL,17,FMarch 2022.
