OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FSofia, who did not want to reveal her
OL,7,Ffull name, told ITV News that she was
OL,8,Fdeported to Anapa, Russia, alongside a
OL,9,Fgroup of other children where she was
OL,10,Fenrolled in a local Russian school and
OL,11,Fwas subjected to alleged bullying.
OL,13,F"We were filmed without consent, and
OL,14,Fthe teacher did not care. I was called
OL,15,Fracist names by Russian students, and
OL,16,Fpunished after shouting 'Glory to
OL,17,FUkraine' in the classroom," she said.
OL,18,FITV News is not able to independently
OL,19,Fverify her claims.
