OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FThe teenager was eventually rescued by
OL,7,Fthe human rights initiative Save
OL,8,FUkraine after her mother contacted the
OL,9,Forganisation.
OL,11,FThe organisation is among many groups
OL,12,Ftrying to help bring as many children
OL,13,Fback as possible.
