OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FOlga Yerokhina, who works for Save
OL,7,FUkraine, told ITV News that children
OL,8,Fwho have been rescued from the camps
OL,9,Fdescribe "being forbidden to speak
OL,10,FUkrainian, being forced to listen to
OL,11,Fthe Russian national anthem , and
OL,12,Fbeing lied to and told their parents
OL,13,Fhad abandoned them."
OL,15,FSome of them end up being placed for
OL,16,Fadoption in Russia, where the process
OL,17,Fhas been expedited to rush the stolen
OL,18,Fchildren through the system, she added.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
