OL,3,CWhy is Russia kidnapping Ukrainian
OL,4,Cchildren?
OL,6,FBritain's ambassador to Ukraine,
OL,7,FMelinda Simmons, said the alleged
OL,8,Fabductions were part of its "hybrid
OL,9,Finvasion" of the country.
OL,11,FChildren taken or kept by Russia were
OL,12,F"subject to an extraordinary,
OL,13,Frelentless range of brainwashing,"
OL,14,FSimmons said, which "creates a
OL,15,Fpsychological barrier between the kids
OL,16,Fand their parents".
